    period: "September 2019 - January 2024",
    description: "Took the university from unfiltered web publishing to user-centred digital products and services that support the university's strategic objectives.",
    achievements: [
      "Championed and implemented user-centred design (UCD) and digital inclusion principles and methodologies",
      "Built relationships with and engaged stakeholders in the UCD process",
      "Supported the development of project goals and planning",
